Reed Diamond https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Reed_Diamond 0 Reed Edward Diamond (born July 20, 1967) is an American actor. He is best known for the roles of Det. Mike Kellerman on Homicide: Life on the Street, Jason Pillar in season 8 of 24, and recurring character Laurence Dominic on Dollhouse. He also appeared in The Shield, Journeyman, Bones, The Mentalist, Franklin Bash, Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D. and Underground. He currently has a recurring role on Designated Survivor as John Foerstel, Director of the FBI. Reed_Edward_Diamond ( born July_20_,_1967 ) is an_American_actor .
